link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536852</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fLDFcUN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfLDFcUN.jpg&h=350c6ca1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9301821c5d044c1d0ee657cf8fd147d3bfd58dcc","tid":1537250,"uid":53364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:19:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9cebd8f63b561499dc5da1711d0836e9979fe939","tid":1537250,"uid":176484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:23:18.000Z","msg":"[律師建議］ 緊急 請廣傳<br />\n<br />\n831太子站當日有份俾人打嘅市民，請盡快聯絡律師做民事訴訟(personal injuries)，向法庭申請要地鐵攞CCTV。<br />\n<br />\n一定要快，如果過咗期限，地鐵話自動洗咗啲CCTV，到時就真係冇人知道太子發生過咩事。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n註：其實唔止身體受傷，心靈受創都可以告。當日喺現場目擊事件，造成精神痛苦，都可以嘗試用 secondary victim （非直接受害人）去追討。最後告唔告得入唔係最重要，目的係令多啲人有權拎CCTV，還原真相⚠️<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n星火同盟 98190979<br />\n民陣 65499452<br />\n民權觀察 94632945<br />\n伍展邦律師行 26081400<br />\n<br />\n推呀！！唔想有人抄車，但更加唔想抄左車但冇人知！！黑警一定要還債<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n追究到底！"}]}